705055f-b.text:
(1)
Hunterfly Place, west side, at and north of Atlantic Ave., to Heric-
imer Street, showing at the corner a former roadhouse of Jacob Noll.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The sawe, showing the east side of Hunterfly Place.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
